Also Ron Rickets now uses a micro controller for his miniboxes. With that, you can control step in Hz, Rate, 
Dwell and track an analog input for a random mode. 

Here is a link with one at pretty low cost.

http://www.arduino.cc/


I don&#39;t know how involved you wanted to get, but i was thinking of using this myself.  I just choose to keep it much simpler, i still get good results.

-Steve H.




